          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Eight 400 mu-g/cm2 thick 141Pr targets (100% natural",
                "enrichment) mounted on a target wheel, rotating",
                "synchronously with the UNILAC macropulsing.The",
                "targets were produced by evaporating the 141PrF3",
                "material onto a carbon backing of 40 mu-g/cm2",
                "thickness and covered with a 10 mu-g/cm2 carbon",
                "layer to increase the radiative cooling."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Velocity separator SHIP with crossed",
                "magnetic and electric fields was used"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "After separation the recoiling evaporation",
                "residues were implanted into a 300 mu-m thick,",
                "35x80 mm2 16-strip position-sensitive silicon",
                "detector, where their subsequentparticle decays were",
                "measured by using standard implantation techniques"
              ]
            }
          ],
